data.title: Find a FairPlay voucher activity provider
data.meta_description: The directory lists the location and details for approved activity providers in the FairPlay voucher program.
data.text:
This is the list of registered activity providers who can accept FairPlay vouchers.

How to search

To find an activity provider, you can search by:

organisation name

type of activity

postcode or suburb.

The Search form will show some suggestion as you are typing. Select your search term from this list. Only organisations that meet all of your search keywords will be displayed.

New registration system

FairPlay has moved to a new online system called Enquire. All activity providers will need to re-apply in the new system. Once new registrations are complete and applications approved, the activity provider directory will be updated.
